title: Xena Warrior Princess (01 - 14) (1999 - 2000)
description:
Xena Warrior Princess (01 - 14) (1999 - 2000) 


That's right, baby, the hit television show is once again a comic, but this time, done the right way! Join Xena and Gabrielle as they wander the lands of ancient Earth, waging war on the powers of evil and oppression every month. Featuring the prose abilities of John Wagner (Judge Dredd) and the artistic excellence of Joyce Chin (Xena) and Walden Wong
